I used intellji to create this project as I started using it instead of eclipse recently and have found it alot more user friendly and more suited to me.
I tried to make this software as unbreakable as possible and has become my most proud project as a result.
Commas can be used to seperate data members for example cast and genre when creating new items.
The program lays the foundation for an effective application for browsing and playing movies.
This system could be extended by integrating a video player which allows you to play videos from your library.